(28714, 'Uni alpha oral pwd. 10 sachets', 'يوني الفا 10 كيس', '', '106', 'Gelatin (collagen) hydrolysate+vitamin c', 'Debeiky > maxare', 'Sachet', 'أكياس', '', 'Antirheumatic.osteoarthritis.anabolic agents', '', 'Gelatin is used for weight loss and for treating osteoarthritis, rheumatoid arthritis, and brittle bones (osteoporosis). Some people also use it for strengthening bones, joints, and fingernails. Gelatin is also used for improving hair condition and to shorten the recovery after exercise and sports-related injury [L2113]. Gelatin is used in preparations of foods, cosmetics, and medicine [L2113].
